OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain to start the
OL,7,Fevening, but clearing from the west
OL,8,Fovernight with clear periods
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Breezy at first but winds
OL,10,Fgenerally falling light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry and bright through the
OL,13,Fmorning, then becoming mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fduring the afternoon with a few
OL,15,Fshowers moving across the area.
OL,16,FClearer spells overnight may lead to a
OL,17,Fpatchy frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
