OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLargely
OL,6,Fdry with bright or sunny spells on
OL,7,FSunday. Cloudier on Monday and Tuesday
OL,8,Fwith showers spreading inland from
OL,9,Fcoastal areas. Feeling cooler,
OL,10,Fespecially along windward coastal
OL,11,Fdistricts.
